title: Taraful din clejani, old recordings - 1949/1952
description:
Taraful din Clejani - muzica de colectie vol.?

This one is for hardcore fans only!
Old stuff - very badly recorded - oldfashion technology - be warned!
We are talking roumania before ceaucescu, 1949-52.
I don't know's playing, but i suspect it is some of the old guys from taraf de haidouks (at least the same village: clejani). Could somebody perhaps fill me in on the missing details...?
